snippet.title: Official Reveal Trailer | PAW Patrol Academy | PAW Patrol
snippet.description:
After 70+ (dog) years as leaders of the pack, PAW Patrol is embarking on a new mission: design the first-ever learning app for PAWsome preschool families that prepares kids for their first classroom.  Sign up to learn more at www.pawpatrolacademy.com.

With heroic missions and engaging lessons featuring real show clips from the #1 preschool brand, PAW Patrol AcademyTM offers age-appropriate, interactive adventures that capture a child’s full attention.  Designed for ages 2-5, with activities that tackle subjects like spelling, numbers, shapes, music, coloring and more, PAW Patrol Academy invites your child inside Adventure Bay like never before, deepening their love of learning and accelerating their development and growth.

Launching this Fall for iOS and Android devices, PAW Patrol Academy’s self-guided activities also ensures guilt-free, productive screen time for kids, freeing up parents to tackle their own To Do lists.  Join the mailing list at www.pawpatrolacademy.com to be the first to know what's ahead.

PAW Patrol Academy is being developed by Originator, a leader in educational mobile apps for kids and families and a wholly owned division of Spin Master.

#PAWPatrol #PAWPatrolAcademy #LearningUnleashed #preschoolapp #preschoolearning
